body:
@taylorswift I‘m so thankful to have you in my life, you always make me feel okay even when I‘m down. I hope someday I’ll get the chance to tell you in person how much you help me and that you’re the reason why I didn’t give up on myself. I love you from the bottom of my heart and I wouldn’t be who I am today without you. Please never stop being yourself and making me smile. ♥️


@taylornation 🌹🐍

Me: I just really love Taylor Swift
